    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for long-term chassis rigidity. It sits on a revised suspension setup with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the communicative steering and balanced weight distribution remain sharp. The exterior retains a clean aesthetic with minor patina consistent with its mileage, while the powertrain remains thermally stable and mechanically sound.",
